The paper deals with approximation algorithms for a facility location problem, which involves optimization and combinatorial aspects. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories, such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.AL (Computational Geometry), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
